WEBVTT

01:35.680 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:37.800 --> 01:43.560
BEFORE SENIOR YEAR INTERNSHIP

01:49.400 --> 01:51.000
Your name is unlucky.

01:51.080 --> 01:52.640
See, you keep losing.

01:54.040 --> 01:55.640
Your name screams "fail" and "surrender".

01:57.120 --> 01:58.360
Oh no.

01:58.440 --> 02:01.520
Should the character in your name
be pronounced "xiang" or "jiang"?

02:04.840 --> 02:05.960
It's "jiang".

02:06.040 --> 02:07.360
BAI JIANG

02:07.440 --> 02:09.680
Then you typed it wrong.
Shouldn't you use another "jiang"?

02:13.440 --> 02:14.480
That "jiang" was already taken.

02:15.400 --> 02:18.160
Right. I might stop
playing this game soon.

02:18.800 --> 02:20.720
Internship's starting soon.
Things are getting busy.

02:22.160 --> 02:24.400
I just didn't want you
waiting for me to team up,

02:24.480 --> 02:26.520
so I'm telling you ahead of time.

02:27.920 --> 02:29.280
I'll reach out when I'm free.

02:35.600 --> 02:36.560
Okay.

02:42.280 --> 02:43.200
Then,

02:43.880 --> 02:46.360
she really never came online again.

02:51.640 --> 02:55.160
TWO YEARS LATER

03:06.120 --> 03:07.400
YOUR FRIEND WARM WATER IS ONLINE

03:21.440 --> 03:22.720
Long time no see.

03:25.760 --> 03:27.080
You're still playing this game?

03:28.080 --> 03:29.320
I'm clearing my phone storage

03:29.400 --> 03:31.080
and suddenly saw this game,

03:31.160 --> 03:32.400
so I logged in to take a look.

03:35.320 --> 03:38.120
Yeah, how have you been?

03:39.720 --> 03:40.600
Not so great.

03:41.760 --> 03:43.600
Life isn't exactly happy,

03:43.680 --> 03:45.440
but I just get by.

03:48.280 --> 03:50.280
I've got something to do.
I'm logging off now.

03:50.360 --> 03:51.240
See you.

04:09.040 --> 04:11.920
APRIL 7TH, NANWU TO YIHE

04:12.000 --> 04:14.120
CABIN SELECTION

04:18.839 --> 04:25.080
YIHE

04:25.160 --> 04:26.040
Hello, ma'am.

04:26.120 --> 04:27.280
You're here, young man.

04:27.360 --> 04:28.400
Hold on.

04:31.760 --> 04:32.720
Here you go,
all your papers for the month.

04:32.800 --> 04:33.640
Not a single issue missing.

04:33.720 --> 04:34.680
Great. Thanks.

04:35.520 --> 04:36.520
I've always wondered,

04:36.600 --> 04:38.400
why don't you subscribe online?

04:38.480 --> 04:40.880
Instead, you fly to Yihe
every month to pick them up.

04:41.400 --> 04:43.280
I come to look around anyway,
so it's no trouble.

04:43.840 --> 04:44.920
Thanks again.

04:51.040 --> 04:52.360
Hello, Mr. Chen.

04:52.440 --> 04:54.800
Yes, I'm a reporter from Yihe Daily.

04:54.880 --> 04:56.200
About the issue yesterday,

04:56.280 --> 04:58.800
the group wage protest,
could I interview you briefly?

04:58.880 --> 05:00.400
Yes, just a few simple questions.

05:16.120 --> 05:16.960
4,062 DAYS

05:34.600 --> 05:35.640
Sang Yan…

05:39.880 --> 05:41.280
Why are you so unlucky?

05:44.680 --> 05:45.840
How am I unlucky?

05:49.320 --> 05:51.560
You always run into bad luck.

05:56.840 --> 05:58.360
Did you

05:59.160 --> 06:01.200
do something terrible to me
in your past life?

06:01.920 --> 06:02.880
Like what?

06:08.680 --> 06:09.960
For example,

06:12.680 --> 06:14.600
maybe when I was 70 or 80,

06:15.400 --> 06:17.080
still unmarried,

06:19.800 --> 06:22.480
and finally an old man
fell in love with me.

06:24.040 --> 06:25.880
Then, on our wedding night,

06:26.880 --> 06:28.680
he ran away with you.

06:31.320 --> 06:32.760
So, this lifetime,

06:35.960 --> 06:37.760
I'm here just to annoy you.

06:43.600 --> 06:45.000
Then I'll repay the debt.

06:46.000 --> 06:48.280
In this life, can you treat me better?

06:49.440 --> 06:50.640
What debt?

06:55.120 --> 06:56.880
Didn't I owe you a man?

06:59.240 --> 07:01.040
How about I repay you with myself?

07:06.560 --> 07:07.640
Is that okay?

07:11.160 --> 07:12.600
That's fine.

07:13.400 --> 07:17.000
But… didn't you owe me an old man?

07:19.280 --> 07:20.120
Alright.

07:21.320 --> 07:23.000
Then, let's leave it for now.

07:23.920 --> 07:25.160
Wait for…

07:25.720 --> 07:28.120
about 40 years, or 50 years.

07:32.480 --> 07:33.640
I will repay you then.

07:42.320 --> 07:44.120
Did you listen
to the doctor's instructions? carefully?

07:45.800 --> 07:46.760
Of course.

07:47.560 --> 07:50.520
Change the dressing after one week.
Stitches out in two weeks.

07:52.200 --> 07:53.720
Any food you need to avoid?

07:54.520 --> 07:55.360
No.

07:56.600 --> 07:58.800
But I definitely need

07:58.880 --> 08:01.120
Shuangjiang, Yifan, and Dian's company.

08:01.720 --> 08:03.280
Then, isn't that even worse?

08:05.160 --> 08:07.600
The injury isn't that serious.

08:08.120 --> 08:09.080
No need to exaggerate it.

08:09.800 --> 08:11.200
I'll look it up myself.

08:15.600 --> 08:17.120
Wen Shuangjiang,

08:17.680 --> 08:19.920
you're pretty harsh to your patient now.

08:22.200 --> 08:23.400
Harsh?

08:23.480 --> 08:24.480
I was worried you wouldn't notice.

08:25.280 --> 08:26.880
You usually never lose your temper.

08:26.960 --> 08:27.960
Why so fierce today?

08:29.480 --> 08:31.040
I told you I'd get angry.

08:32.320 --> 08:33.880
You're still mad?

08:33.960 --> 08:36.360
Didn't we already make up at the hospital?

08:38.159 --> 08:39.720
Why are you bringing this up again now?

08:51.120 --> 08:52.040
I haven't forgiven you yet.

09:14.560 --> 09:15.600
Sang Yan,

09:16.960 --> 09:19.120
I just want to protect you properly.

09:52.000 --> 09:52.840
Here.

10:11.000 --> 10:12.360
Take your medicine.

10:12.440 --> 10:13.760
I'll watch you take it.

10:35.960 --> 10:38.040
Aren't you sleepy? Get some rest first.

10:42.320 --> 10:43.320
Then I'll go take a shower.

10:45.000 --> 10:46.920
Your wound can't get wet now.

10:47.000 --> 10:48.800
I know. I'll just wipe myself down.

11:03.920 --> 11:05.400
Wen Shuangjiang,

11:06.760 --> 11:07.800
how much longer will you stick to me?

11:09.040 --> 11:11.400
I just… want to see…

11:11.920 --> 11:13.440
if there's anything I can do to help.

11:15.120 --> 11:17.560
Didn't I just say I was going to shower?

11:18.160 --> 11:19.240
What can you help me with?

11:21.520 --> 11:25.120
- Well, I could.
- Could what? Just go to bed.

11:25.200 --> 11:26.160
No need for your help.

11:26.240 --> 11:28.440
- What if your wound opens up?
- I'll be careful.

11:28.520 --> 11:30.560
I'll take care. Goodnight.

11:31.440 --> 11:33.720
Then… be very careful, please.

11:33.800 --> 11:35.440
- Okay.
- Call me if you need anything.

11:35.520 --> 11:36.360
Got it.

11:59.360 --> 12:00.560
What are you doing?

12:02.240 --> 12:03.640
I'm going to help you shower.

12:05.560 --> 12:06.960
Now it's "I'm going to",

12:07.040 --> 12:08.520
not just "I want to", huh?

12:31.240 --> 12:32.080
I'll help you.

12:52.000 --> 12:54.520
I was just worried you wouldn't
reach your back easily.

12:54.600 --> 12:56.280
You wouldn't clean it yourself.

13:09.600 --> 13:12.320
If you accidentally get your wound wet,

13:12.400 --> 13:14.040
that'd just make things worse.

13:29.120 --> 13:31.640
But even if you're not embarrassed, I am.

13:33.880 --> 13:35.040
I'll do it myself.

13:37.120 --> 13:38.480
Then…

13:38.560 --> 13:39.800
just wipe your legs by yourself.

13:42.800 --> 13:44.880
And then get ready to sleep.

13:47.200 --> 13:49.160
Sleeping this early?

13:49.760 --> 13:51.240
Weren't you wide awake just now?

13:53.920 --> 13:55.160
Do you think

13:55.240 --> 13:57.640
I'm useless now just because I'm injured?

13:58.760 --> 14:00.200
Isn't that true, though?

14:01.480 --> 14:02.600
I'm not exactly useful myself.

14:02.680 --> 14:03.760
I'll go shower.

14:11.840 --> 14:13.280
What exactly is on your mind?

14:17.600 --> 14:18.760
What about you?

14:20.080 --> 14:21.120
Can I have a kiss?

14:28.320 --> 14:29.280
Please?

14:31.240 --> 14:32.520
Well, I suppose that's fine.

14:37.240 --> 14:39.520
You should… lift your head a bit.

14:43.040 --> 14:43.880
A little higher.

15:29.920 --> 15:31.240
Breaking news from our station.

15:31.320 --> 15:32.560
The highly publicized murder case

15:32.640 --> 15:34.120
in Nanwu and Beiyu cities

15:34.200 --> 15:35.600
has been solved.

15:36.480 --> 15:39.720
The suspect, Che Xingde,
has confessed to all crimes.

15:39.800 --> 15:41.520
Nanwu police announced

15:41.600 --> 15:43.200
that solving this case

15:43.280 --> 15:45.560
strongly upholds social justice

15:46.240 --> 15:47.440
and brings significant comfort

15:47.520 --> 15:49.640
to the victims and their families.

15:57.240 --> 16:00.760
Currently, Che Xingde has been…

16:05.520 --> 16:06.400
Currently,

16:06.480 --> 16:08.920
Che Xingde has been placed
under criminal detention,

16:09.000 --> 16:11.320
with court proceedings underway.

16:11.400 --> 16:13.880
Authorities remain committed
to thoroughly investigating,

16:13.960 --> 16:16.440
ensuring comprehensive public safety,

16:16.520 --> 16:19.040
and protecting the lives
and property of citizens.

16:20.680 --> 16:22.560
Stay tuned for more updates.

16:28.240 --> 16:31.600
Defendant,
do you have any final statements?

17:06.920 --> 17:07.760
Guo Ling.

17:08.280 --> 17:09.359
Mr. Che.

17:10.000 --> 17:11.880
Why are you here so late at night?

17:12.520 --> 17:13.880
I'm fine.

17:19.079 --> 17:20.359
Then why are you crying?

17:21.480 --> 17:22.480
My dad…

17:24.160 --> 17:25.880
doesn't support my writing.

17:28.319 --> 17:30.160
You argued with him because of that?

17:32.560 --> 17:33.840
What did you write?

17:34.560 --> 17:35.680
Can I have a look?

17:40.520 --> 17:41.880
Sure.

18:08.440 --> 18:09.400
De!

18:10.640 --> 18:11.480
De!

18:12.440 --> 18:13.680
- Sis!
- De!

18:13.760 --> 18:14.880
Sis, over here!

19:01.080 --> 19:02.560
You really killed her?

19:05.120 --> 19:06.480
Sis…

19:07.480 --> 19:09.680
Keep your voice down! Now, what do we do?

19:09.760 --> 19:11.160
You're crazy!

19:11.240 --> 19:13.240
Why would you kill someone?

19:13.320 --> 19:15.040
- You're insane!
- I didn't mean to!

19:15.120 --> 19:17.280
Sis, please calm down! Stop crying!

19:17.360 --> 19:19.400
Stop it! Sis,

19:20.360 --> 19:22.280
in this world, you're the only family
I have left, aren't you?

19:24.120 --> 19:25.360
You loved me most when we were little.

19:25.440 --> 19:27.080
Please help me find a way out.

19:27.160 --> 19:28.640
You have to help me, sis! If you don't,

19:28.720 --> 19:30.240
I won't survive!

19:30.840 --> 19:32.960
Sis, please. I'm begging you. Sis, please.

19:35.160 --> 19:37.280
I'll even kneel to you. I'm begging you.

19:37.360 --> 19:39.440
Please! Please help me!

19:39.520 --> 19:41.240
Mom and Dad are gone. You're my only hope!

20:00.000 --> 20:01.480
I'm sorry to Guo Ling.

20:02.720 --> 20:04.800
I'm sorry to Zeng Yi.

20:06.480 --> 20:08.160
And I'm sorry…

20:14.800 --> 20:17.240
to all those girls I hurt.

20:18.840 --> 20:20.800
I couldn't control myself,

20:20.880 --> 20:23.360
and I turned their youth into a nightmare.

20:25.880 --> 20:27.400
The crimes I've committed…

20:29.920 --> 20:31.120
are unforgivable.

20:32.200 --> 20:33.520
I deserve death.

20:41.840 --> 20:43.080
I plead guilty.

20:49.280 --> 20:50.400
This court declares.

20:51.200 --> 20:54.120
According to the Criminal Law
of the People's Republic of China,

20:54.200 --> 20:56.720
Article 232,

20:56.800 --> 20:59.040
Article 236,

20:59.120 --> 21:01.200
Article 237,

21:01.280 --> 21:02.880
Article 69,

21:02.960 --> 21:05.800
and Article 307,

21:05.880 --> 21:07.280
the verdict is as follows…

21:08.040 --> 21:09.400
All rise!

21:16.160 --> 21:19.800
Defendant Che Xingde,
for intentional homicide,

21:19.880 --> 21:23.600
is sentenced to death
and deprived of political rights for life.

21:24.120 --> 21:25.840
For rape,

21:25.920 --> 21:28.000
sentenced to ten years in prison.

21:28.880 --> 21:30.960
For sexual assault,

21:31.480 --> 21:33.800
sentenced to three years imprisonment.

21:33.880 --> 21:35.200
Combining these sentences,

21:35.280 --> 21:36.920
he is sentenced to death

21:37.000 --> 21:39.360
and deprived of political rights for life.

21:40.760 --> 21:42.360
Defendant Che Yanqin,

21:42.440 --> 21:45.680
for destroying and fabricating evidence,

21:45.760 --> 21:47.840
is sentenced to three years imprisonment.

21:52.840 --> 21:56.200
BEIYU

22:09.920 --> 22:10.800
Yifan,

22:11.760 --> 22:14.000
you've followed this story for so long.

22:14.080 --> 22:16.720
Today, it finally ends, right?

22:18.400 --> 22:19.800
It's finally over.

22:27.840 --> 22:29.000
It's really over.

22:34.440 --> 22:36.720
It's time to leave
it behind in my life, too.

22:53.600 --> 22:55.000
It's okay.

22:57.440 --> 22:59.080
The boy you like

23:00.440 --> 23:01.640
will think you're brave, too.

23:02.920 --> 23:06.120
He'll thank you for protecting yourself.

23:34.560 --> 23:35.600
Ling,

23:36.200 --> 23:38.120
I'm sorry.

23:41.720 --> 23:42.920
It took me so long

23:43.640 --> 23:46.080
to finally bring you back home.

24:03.720 --> 24:05.280
Hello, Mr. Guo?

24:05.360 --> 24:06.720
I should thank you

24:07.400 --> 24:09.840
for your dedication,

24:09.920 --> 24:12.600
which finally brought out the truth.

24:13.880 --> 24:16.520
On behalf of Guo Ling, thank you.

24:17.560 --> 24:19.080
It's my responsibility.

24:21.520 --> 24:22.800
For Ling…

24:28.360 --> 24:29.680
and for myself.

24:31.840 --> 24:33.400
Solving this case

24:33.480 --> 24:35.840
strongly upholds social justice

24:36.520 --> 24:37.680
and brings significant comfort

24:37.760 --> 24:39.600
- to the victims and their families.
- …is sentenced to death

24:39.680 --> 24:41.200
and deprived of political rights for life.

24:41.280 --> 24:43.560
I, Che Xingde,

24:43.640 --> 24:47.640
confess to committing the crimes of murder

24:48.160 --> 24:49.360
and rape over the past years.

24:51.480 --> 24:53.640
I accept

24:53.720 --> 24:54.800
all legal punishment.

25:19.200 --> 25:20.080
Yan!

25:22.040 --> 25:23.880
Uh, there's something I need to tell you.

25:28.920 --> 25:32.760
NETEASE GAMES

25:32.840 --> 25:33.880
Got it.

25:36.040 --> 25:36.880
See you.

25:40.000 --> 25:41.360
Hello, ma'am.

25:41.960 --> 25:43.680
My phone ends in 1024.

25:46.840 --> 25:48.600
Your stepsister asked me to tell you,

25:48.680 --> 25:51.560
if you have time, could you visit her?

25:54.080 --> 25:55.240
Will you go?

26:00.920 --> 26:01.760
I don't plan to.

26:05.240 --> 26:07.280
- Want to eat?
- Of course.

26:13.280 --> 26:15.960
Ouch, my hand really is…

26:44.800 --> 26:47.000
EARTHLY DELIGHTS: LINLONG MARKET

26:47.080 --> 26:50.640
Guo Ling's dad called me again today.

26:50.720 --> 26:51.760
What did he say?

26:52.440 --> 26:54.000
He said

26:54.080 --> 26:56.080
he appreciates my honest reporting

26:56.160 --> 26:58.400
and the effort I put in.

26:59.280 --> 27:00.560
Something along those lines.

27:02.720 --> 27:04.880
But I just see it as my job.

27:06.560 --> 27:07.800
Those aren't mutually exclusive.

27:07.880 --> 27:09.200
It's your job,

27:09.280 --> 27:10.920
but people can still thank you.

27:16.200 --> 27:18.080
Actually, I used to…

27:19.480 --> 27:21.760
not really like being a reporter.

27:22.840 --> 27:23.680
Why not?

27:25.440 --> 27:27.120
It's not about the industry.

27:28.640 --> 27:30.760
I just felt nothing mattered,

27:30.840 --> 27:32.120
except dancing.

27:33.800 --> 27:36.040
Then, why did you go to grad school?

27:37.040 --> 27:39.000
To better myself.

27:39.080 --> 27:40.240
Those are two separate things.

27:42.760 --> 27:44.840
Maybe you started liking this job.

27:49.560 --> 27:50.400
Sang Yan,

27:52.400 --> 27:54.160
have you ever thought about this?

27:54.840 --> 27:56.280
If one day we could go somewhere

27:56.360 --> 27:58.120
no one knows us,

27:59.520 --> 28:01.640
even change our names,

28:04.440 --> 28:07.800
could we forget the past and start fresh?

28:10.560 --> 28:13.720
Is that why you left
without telling me twice?

28:16.800 --> 28:17.840
The first time, I didn't know
how to handle things.

28:20.640 --> 28:21.880
I thought you deserved someone better.

28:23.280 --> 28:24.280
What about the second time?

28:26.520 --> 28:27.840
Regarding the second time…

28:28.840 --> 28:31.040
I thought if I left,

28:31.120 --> 28:32.520
he wouldn't have any reason to hurt you.

28:35.520 --> 28:36.640
I get it.

28:38.200 --> 28:39.640
You wanted to protect me.

28:46.680 --> 28:51.120
But later, I also sympathized
with those who wanted to vanish.

28:51.200 --> 28:54.080
Maybe only by doing that
could they find courage to start again.

28:56.480 --> 28:58.120
If that's true,

28:58.200 --> 29:02.040
then I should thank you
for your time in Hong Kong, China.

29:07.080 --> 29:09.200
The only thing I couldn't let go of…

29:12.120 --> 29:13.200
was you.

29:15.960 --> 29:16.880
I know.

29:17.400 --> 29:18.400
Know what?

29:19.160 --> 29:20.800
That you can't get over me,

29:20.880 --> 29:22.160
and that I'm amazing.

29:22.240 --> 29:24.320
You're still so cocky.

29:27.240 --> 29:28.520
Wen Shuangjiang,

29:29.120 --> 29:30.280
do you want to dance again?

29:32.120 --> 29:34.040
If we went back a few years,

29:35.440 --> 29:36.520
probably yes.

29:37.720 --> 29:38.760
And now?

29:41.120 --> 29:42.320
Now…

29:43.400 --> 29:46.240
After finishing the article
on Che Xingde's case last night,

29:46.800 --> 29:48.240
and then getting a call

29:48.320 --> 29:49.920
from Guo Ling's dad today,

29:52.880 --> 29:54.320
I suddenly realized

29:55.280 --> 29:57.840
I really love being a reporter.

30:01.400 --> 30:02.560
As long as you're happy.

30:05.360 --> 30:06.560
From now on,

30:06.640 --> 30:08.320
you'll only dance for me.

30:08.400 --> 30:09.360
That's great, too.

30:11.520 --> 30:14.080
Did you always love watching me dance?

30:14.800 --> 30:16.560
You just realized?

30:16.640 --> 30:18.000
And what if I stop dancing now?

30:18.760 --> 30:19.920
So what?

30:20.000 --> 30:21.320
I like you no matter what.

30:22.040 --> 30:23.080
What do you want to eat?

30:25.760 --> 30:26.960
I just saw…

30:30.920 --> 30:32.240
I'll take this.

30:32.320 --> 30:33.560
Hi. One pack, please.

30:33.640 --> 30:34.880
NOUGAT CANDY

30:34.960 --> 30:35.800
Thank you.

30:38.160 --> 30:39.360
I've paid. Thanks.

30:41.280 --> 30:43.120
The packaging is pretty nice.

30:47.560 --> 30:48.400
Want some?

30:49.720 --> 30:50.560
Then I'll have one.

30:54.360 --> 30:55.200
It tastes pretty good.

30:56.520 --> 30:57.640
It's not too sweet and very milky.

30:58.760 --> 31:01.000
Your standards for good candy are weird.

31:02.200 --> 31:03.040
"Not sweet"?

31:03.760 --> 31:04.600
Let me try it.

31:20.920 --> 31:22.000
You tricked me.

31:22.560 --> 31:23.840
This is sweet enough.

31:24.440 --> 31:25.920
You need to chew it, too.

31:27.600 --> 31:28.640
It's nougat.

31:28.720 --> 31:30.200
Chew it to taste the milkiness.

31:31.080 --> 31:33.560
It has nothing to do with chewing.

31:34.080 --> 31:35.080
Get it?

31:38.240 --> 31:39.360
What are you looking for?

31:56.000 --> 31:56.840
Oh, right.

31:57.800 --> 31:58.960
The landlady said

31:59.040 --> 32:00.960
she wants the place back.

32:01.040 --> 32:03.080
We have to move out by next March.

32:04.840 --> 32:06.520
Next March?

32:07.600 --> 32:10.560
So, we only have
six more months of dating.

32:11.720 --> 32:14.040
- Huh?
- What?

32:14.600 --> 32:16.280
Aren't we doing fine?

32:16.360 --> 32:17.960
How come we only have six months left?

32:19.240 --> 32:20.560
What are you thinking?

32:20.640 --> 32:22.120
Is that what I meant?

32:28.520 --> 32:31.160
Why do you talk in riddles now?

32:37.320 --> 32:39.280
I've never paid attention
to other couples.

32:39.920 --> 32:41.000
Usually,

32:41.840 --> 32:43.680
how long do people date

32:43.760 --> 32:44.600
before getting married?

32:45.520 --> 32:47.000
Usually pretty quick,

32:47.080 --> 32:48.920
days or weeks even.

32:49.000 --> 32:50.440
We're already pretty slow.

32:51.600 --> 32:52.720
Way too slow.

32:53.640 --> 32:55.600
Then, let's date another year or two.

32:58.040 --> 32:59.880
You want it longer, huh?

32:59.960 --> 33:02.240
Sure, as long as it's with me.

33:20.320 --> 33:21.760
Do you want to dance again?

33:22.440 --> 33:24.680
If we went back a few years,

33:25.720 --> 33:26.880
probably yes.

33:29.200 --> 33:30.440
Why did it take me until now

33:31.040 --> 33:32.720
to truly understand?

33:41.400 --> 33:43.720
So, I should give up dancing now?

33:45.520 --> 33:47.760
No one could bear the pain

33:48.480 --> 33:50.040
you went through
during your high school years.

33:53.440 --> 33:54.960
The day my Shuangjiang…

33:57.640 --> 33:59.960
had her wings broken by someone else.

34:10.760 --> 34:11.719
Wen Shuangjiang,

34:14.040 --> 34:15.520
I'm saying this

34:15.600 --> 34:18.320
because I want to stay with you forever.

34:19.080 --> 34:20.520
Aside from changing your boyfriend,

34:20.600 --> 34:23.000
I'll support you
in whatever you want to do.

34:25.320 --> 34:28.800
Don't settle for less, okay?

34:30.520 --> 34:32.480
We still have plenty of time.

34:32.560 --> 34:34.199
It's never too late

34:35.000 --> 34:36.120
to start anything.

34:36.199 --> 34:37.719
Just do whatever you want.

34:39.520 --> 34:40.880
Got it?

34:45.120 --> 34:46.080
Sang Yan,

34:47.320 --> 34:49.080
I'm different now.

34:50.520 --> 34:52.280
I used to be weak,

34:52.360 --> 34:53.520
with no one to rely on.

34:55.320 --> 34:58.280
But now, I can do whatever I want,

34:59.080 --> 35:01.080
without worrying about others.

35:05.240 --> 35:06.520
Because I have you now.

35:08.640 --> 35:12.360
And I've realized
I truly like being a journalist.

35:13.200 --> 35:16.000
I've dedicated myself to this job
all these years.

35:16.640 --> 35:19.960
If I had to quit now to do something else,

35:20.960 --> 35:22.440
I'd feel unhappy about it.

35:23.320 --> 35:25.000
And I can be like you.

35:25.080 --> 35:26.480
Like me?

35:26.560 --> 35:28.760
Don't you run a gastropub as a side job?

35:29.480 --> 35:31.880
If someday I want to dance again,

35:31.960 --> 35:34.040
I could do it as my side job, too.

35:34.880 --> 35:36.000
That's possible.

35:40.080 --> 35:41.040
Tell me.

35:41.800 --> 35:44.480
Were you sent by my dad
to take care of me?

35:46.320 --> 35:47.240
No,

35:53.120 --> 35:54.440
I volunteered.

36:20.680 --> 36:23.480
If you want to edit the text,
click here, this icon.

36:23.560 --> 36:24.760
Click it once.

36:25.520 --> 36:27.680
Then click again right here.

36:32.400 --> 36:34.280
Yifan, Mr. Gan asked you to see him.

36:34.360 --> 36:36.520
- Got it.
- What did she say?

36:36.600 --> 36:39.040
Mr. Gan asked for me. You try it first.

36:39.120 --> 36:41.040
If there's any problem,
I'll help you when I'm back.

36:45.800 --> 36:48.760
Last year's event was okay,

36:48.840 --> 36:50.800
but we can't do the same thing every year.

36:52.600 --> 36:54.040
- Mr. Gan.
- Come in.

36:54.120 --> 36:55.680
- You wanted me?
- Yifan,

36:55.760 --> 36:57.760
you studied dance for ten years, right?

36:59.840 --> 37:00.840
The annual party is coming soon,

37:00.920 --> 37:02.080
so prepare a performance

37:02.160 --> 37:04.320
and bring honor to our First News team.

37:04.400 --> 37:06.840
But I haven't danced properly
in a long time.

37:06.920 --> 37:09.400
No worries. It's all about participation.

37:10.000 --> 37:11.160
Please help us out, Yifan.

37:11.240 --> 37:12.800
Just one performance.

37:12.880 --> 37:14.520
I'm afraid I won't have time to practice,

37:15.360 --> 37:17.360
plus, there are
a lot of reports coming up.

37:17.440 --> 37:18.800
No pressure,

37:18.880 --> 37:20.840
just add to the atmosphere.

37:21.440 --> 37:23.920
- Put Yifan down for a performance.
- Got it.

37:24.000 --> 37:25.920
Alright, you can get back to work now.

37:28.960 --> 37:30.040
I'm your brother.

37:30.760 --> 37:32.080
I've eaten more salt than…

37:32.960 --> 37:34.200
than you have.

37:35.840 --> 37:37.400
Why don't Mom and Dad approve?

37:37.480 --> 37:39.120
What do you think? Why wouldn't they?

37:41.120 --> 37:43.760
Honestly, well…

37:43.840 --> 37:45.080
he is a bit older.

37:46.560 --> 37:49.160
Don't get mad. It's just the truth.

37:56.480 --> 37:57.480
Was that Zhi?

37:58.920 --> 38:00.160
What's wrong?

38:01.600 --> 38:04.680
She said she wants to bring
Duan Jiaxu home for New Year holiday,

38:04.760 --> 38:06.920
but our parents don't approve.

38:07.000 --> 38:08.080
Why not?

38:09.000 --> 38:11.280
- They think he's too old.
- Really?

38:13.880 --> 38:15.200
Well, he is from the older generation.

38:20.240 --> 38:21.320
How about…

38:22.240 --> 38:24.800
coming home with me this New Year holiday?

38:29.560 --> 38:32.880
But what if your parents
also disapprove of us?

38:33.640 --> 38:35.320
My parents don't have many requirements
for my partner.

38:35.960 --> 38:37.200
Any girl will do.

38:39.920 --> 38:41.320
Say that again!

38:44.840 --> 38:46.400
So, are you free on the 22nd?

38:47.080 --> 38:47.920
The 22nd?

38:48.000 --> 38:49.640
What's up?

38:49.720 --> 38:52.440
My station is holding a year-end party.

38:54.280 --> 38:55.720
I'm singing with Su Tian.

38:55.800 --> 38:57.360
They said we could bring…

38:58.240 --> 38:59.360
bring family.

39:01.360 --> 39:02.520
Family?

39:03.880 --> 39:05.040
Then your family member has time.

39:06.040 --> 39:06.880
On the 22nd, right?

39:16.960 --> 39:19.240
- Su Tian, are you ready?
- Almost.

39:19.320 --> 39:21.200
Maybe use my phone if you can't fix it.

39:21.280 --> 39:23.440
No way. We need something professional.

39:28.080 --> 39:29.360
Yifan, how's it going? Are you ready yet?

39:29.440 --> 39:30.760
- Almost.
- Okay.

39:31.440 --> 39:32.600
Get ready.

40:30.680 --> 40:34.600
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

40:34.680 --> 40:36.160
They told you, family should stay outside.

40:36.240 --> 40:37.200
They kept saying it.

40:37.280 --> 40:38.400
But you insisted on watching.

40:40.520 --> 40:42.240
Doctor, how's the recovery?

40:42.320 --> 40:44.240
Pretty good so far.

40:44.320 --> 40:45.400
The wound is healing well,

40:45.480 --> 40:47.760
no obvious swelling.

40:47.840 --> 40:49.040
But I'd suggest

40:49.120 --> 40:50.280
coming next week for another check-up,

40:50.360 --> 40:51.960
to see how it's healing

40:52.040 --> 40:54.240
and decide about removing stitches.

40:54.880 --> 40:56.360
Next week?

40:56.440 --> 40:58.000
Next Saturday,

40:59.720 --> 41:01.880
October 24th. Does that work?

41:02.560 --> 41:04.600
First Frost Day… (pronounced Shuangjiang)

41:04.680 --> 41:06.640
That's quite a special date.

41:09.720 --> 41:10.680
I have a call.

41:12.040 --> 41:13.120
Hello?

41:16.520 --> 41:17.920
Next Saturday?

41:21.120 --> 41:22.600
Sorry. I already have plans.

41:22.680 --> 41:23.560
Thanks.

44:16.560 --> 44:17.480
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

44:17.560 --> 44:18.440
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
